data.description: Completed NEW construction home with Fully fenced in yard! This stunning open floor plan is ideally located in the desired city of North Port. 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Fully stocked with upgrades galore including energy-efficient Whirlpool® appliances, spacious granite countertops, brushed nickel hardware and an attached two-car garage. A spacious master suite, a dining area, a spacious backyard as well as lush front yard landscaping. This home also offers a smart garage, you can open and close your garage from anywhere from your phone, you can control your temperature in the home from the convenience from your phone as well. On the side of the home there is also a box that controls the sprinkler system. The bedrooms have carpet while the rest of the home has grey laminate floors. Ceiling fan/lights were put in every room. Close to Shopping, beautiful beaches, shopping, restaurants & the Atlanta Braves Spring Training Stadium.
